text: Adriana Espinosa de los Monteros is an archer from Ecuador. She was born on 18 July 1991. Espinosa competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Adriana EspinozaAdriana ESPINOSA DE LOS MONTEROS == References == Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Archers Category:Olympians for Ecuador Category:Sportspeople from Guayaquil
